Welcome to the Cosmatic Drift Wiki! This is somewhat of a work in progress. 

Articles with no prefix are standard information about the game meachanics and server policy. Articles with the <code>Lore:</code> prefix are articles about the game world. Lore articles are typically written from the prospective of an in-universe wikipedia type website however they may contain knowledge that would not be commonly known in-character. Articles with the <code>IC:</code> prefix are written from an entirely in-universe propsective and your character would have ready access to them in-game. 

