=== Contributing to the wiki ===
To prevent vandalism, the wiki is read-only to the general public. Please request the [[Meta:Writer|Writer]] role on discord by asking in the #lore channel. Anyone whitelisted on the game server will be granted edit access. You must login first using your ss14 account by clicking the "Login" button in the top right  before we gan give you edit access. 

Articles in the Lore and IC namespace need to be approved by staff before they are published. See [[Meta:Contributing]] for more information.

All wiki content is licensed under the terms listed in [[Meta:Copyrights]]. By contributing you agree to make your contribution avalible under those terms.

